- [x] FIXED 2026-07-22 (migration 009): `auth.ts` login/totp SELECT/UPDATE of
      `display_name, theme, language, totp_secret_enc, totp_backup_codes` вЂ” added the columns
      (renamed plaintext `totp_secret`в†’`totp_secret_enc`). Also caught `pdf-receipts.ts`
      SELECTing `h.tagline` (same class of runtime crash) в†’ added `hostels.tagline`.
      вљ пёЏ Migration 009 must be applied to any live DB.
- [x] PARTIAL 2026-07-22: role 'super_admin' (not in users CHECK) removed from the 6
      `requireRole` guards in students.ts вЂ” was a dead literal that never matched. NOTE: those
